# Website Wireframe - 9point75 Woodworks LLC

## Home
- Sticky header with Home, Gallery, About, Contact, and Request a Quote CTA
- Text-driven hero with fresh copy
- Value proposition section
- How It Works section
- Materials and craftsmanship section
- Quiet trust signals including veteran-owned
- Footer with email, location, and social placeholders

## Gallery
- One page with category filters
- Show 10 applicable items at a time
- Load more at the bottom
- Tap a thumbnail to expand it full-screen
- Prioritize mobile usability

## About
- Personal story placeholder
- Craftsmanship philosophy
- One-craftsman process and premium materials

## Contact
- Email and description required
- Budget optional
- Support uploads for inspiration images
- Appointment-only messaging

## Future Expansion
- Owner messaging in admin
- Testimonials
- Project detail pages
